messages.message: Hey England! I'm a big fan of English-french alliances, and I really like your press, so let's crush the German!
Hey France, just wanted to establish comms and see if you wanted to DMZ Bur early on and make a run at one of the low countries?

Hey Italy! Would love to have a peaceful southern border, and I'm happy to keep my fleet builds to a minimum if you keep your fleets east of the Tyrrhenian!

Can we DMZ Piedmont, Gol, and West Med, and agree not to build fleets in Rome and Marseilles?
Hey Germany! That sounds good to me! Would you be willing to bounce me in Burgundy in the spring?
Hey Russia, what are your plans for the north? Hoping we can work together at some point!
Hey Turkey, thought I'd reach out and open comms. Looking forward to the game!
Happy to do that
Hey Austria, just wondering what your plans for the early game are, and if we can work together on anything!
Sounds good, looking forward to working together!
Can we agree to DMZ the channel?
Same! Any news from England?
Not yet, but haven't heard enough to be worried!
Same haha

Hey France! Just reaching out to say I'm always happy to share information with my French friends, and I'd love to see if we can work together. It depends a lot on Italy for me -- I can't let a juggernaut form and would be very relieved if you can head east with me.
We can definitely talk about how we'd like to play England going forward
That sounds good to me! I'll see what I can do, but am still working out how the west will shake out. I'll keep you posted!
Sounds good!
Thanks -- I'll let you know if I hear anything juicy.
I would rather work with you then England, so if I get anything I'll let you know
Just so you know, Austria seems to be worried about a juggernaut.
I may be willing to let you have Bel
Thanks!

Yeah, I agree!

As for Belgium, I'd definitely take it, if you're willing!
Let's see how this year goes and decide based on England's opening!
Yep!
Just so you know, Austria seems very worried about a juggernaut.
Austria is very worried about you guys doing a juggernaut. Not sure how true that is, but be careful!
Have you heard anything from Italy? I have reached out to him but no word
Nothing yet, but it's still pretty early.
True

I will still keep out of your territory if you want to work together against Germany. But I really need you to start talking, otherwise I can't trust that you're with me!

Well, I have to say I was expecting you to attack me...especially after the talk of you and Austria working together.

Hopefully we can still work together against England. What are your thoughts?
France what are you doing?

Well, you can definitely move Ankara into the Black Sea now. But I would also suggest moving Smyrna to Armenia. You can't let Austria take Sevastopol.

You should also talk to Russia about working together against Austria.
Nice turn! You're in great shape.
I really don't want to fight you, if you just move back we can have peace. England is a sitting duck
What do you mean?
We have him surrounded, it's over for him
Where do you propose I move?
Thanks! I honestly can't believe nobody is attacking me.
Can I count on you to stay out of the Western Med and the Gulf of Lyon? I have enough on my plate with Germany and England, and I'd really prefer not to worry about you!
You can take the channel, and move into position for Irish Sea and he's done
Also, you might consider moving Venice to Tyrolia and Rome to Venice.
Yeah, but where do you propose I move?
I take the North Sea and the is over
Well, I'm always up for working with other players who aren't attacking me. If you want to team up in the near future, I'm all for it!
I'd strongly suggest talking to Turkey if you aren't already!
The channel and Irish
Sounds good! I need to deal with a non-talking Russia and Turkey first, but then I can be helpful.
And how do I know you won't take Belgium?
